{"tid":653230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支聯會洗刷國殤之柱 何俊仁料劉霞錄音增六四晚會人數","createTime":"2018-05-04T13:56:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T05:34:23.000Z","uid":33890,"like":3,"dislike":79,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"2e5a967229a1ce59c505118ed1f146e2478d3a84","tid":653230,"uid":33890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T13:56:41.000Z","msg":"支聯會主席何俊仁、以及一眾成員共10多人，今（4日）到香港大學黃克競樓平台洗刷「國殤之柱」，並在儀式前默哀及獻花，以悼念六四死難者。<br />\n已故諾貝爾和平獎得主劉曉波遺孀劉霞，日前與流亡德國的內地作家廖亦武的一段錄音對話在維權網站曝光。何俊仁表示，對於錄音內容感到痛心，亦相信全世界人民聽到錄音後都會反感，冀中國政府不會攔阻劉霞到德國治療抑鬱症，否則劉霞以死抗命，中國將會成為劊子手。何俊仁續指，相信劉霞的事件會引起公眾關注，參與六四晚會的人數因此而上升，惟當中最希望年青人出席能參與晚會，認識當年歷史。<br />\n<br />\n支聯會: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f519c89058f551e1e8fea3650bc12564c90581d2","tid":653230,"uid":67346,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T13:57:47.000Z","msg":"一年一度人血饅頭大食會又開始喇"},{"pid":"816ae920f5c375f2a3682d69f2105be57083bce0","tid":653230,"uid":47359,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T14:12:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/221206_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F221206_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=d569a53f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f2f62fa491645fb5db332d5b579230d282cc0cd","tid":653230,"uid":47359,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T14:12:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/221254_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F221254_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=967b1fa9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5def735307754222489c94bff46f775bae9ca6c8","tid":653230,"uid":86841,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"rep